For the best speed set your upload to 50% of your download.  If you average say 1.0 Mbps on download once it finds peers then set your upload to 500 Kbps.  Sometimes you may spend more bandwidth on uploading than downloading but in the long run you will download faster.  The number of peers you are allowed to download from is proportionate to your upload.
